"20:113:10" : {s: 20, a: 113, w: 10, r: "وقي", t: "يَتَّقُونَ", l: "ٱتَّقَىٰ", lc: 166, tl: "yattaqūna", lb: "কোনো কিছুর ব্যাপারে অত্যন্ত সচেতন থাকা, আল্লাহর প্রতি সচেতন থাকা",e: "fear", b: "তাকওয়া অবলম্বন করবে", i: "mereka bertakwa", f: 18, rm: "to protect, save, preserve, ward off, guard against evil and calamity, be secure, take as a shield, regard the duty. muttaqii - one who guard against evil and against that which harms and injures and is regardful of his duty towards human beings and God.", ag: "فعل مضارع صيغة ٨ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Imperfect 8th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "(VIII)", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "ٱتَّقَىٰ"},
